Articles.Content:
Whenever I load up the Orbiting 101 Tutorial, I get this Error Message:
Vessel Loading Error

Vesssel Orbiter 1A was not loaded because it had the following parts missing:
Rockomax16.BW

Is there any way to fix this issue?

20 minutes ago, eatpantboio said:

Whenever I load up the Orbiting 101 Tutorial, I get this Error Message:
Vessel Loading Error

Vesssel Orbiter 1A was not loaded because it had the following parts missing:
Rockomax16.BW

Is there any way to fix this issue?

If you are on Steam go to Library->Right Click Kerbal->Properties->Local Files->Verify Integrity of Game Files.

It will take a while and it will download any missing/corrupted files.

Or else maybe a clean install?Make sure you backup the saves folder first.
